{
  "id": "propak-asia-2026-summary",
  "title": "ProPak Asia 2026 参展总结报告",
  "date": "2026-06-14",
  "tag": "展会总结",
  "summary": "基于72张现场照片的系统性参展复盘：涵盖展台设计、搭建物流、电气设备、撤展打包、友商竞品观察、创意细节收集六大维度，提炼可执行的经验教训与未来改进建议。",
  "category": "展会总结",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "h2",
      "text": "一、展台设计与灯光"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "本届 ProPak Asia 展台设计呈现出几个明显趋势：白色为主色调、充足的灯光配置、简洁开放的空间布局。"
    },
    {
      "type": "h3",
      "text": "1.1 优秀案例：白色+灯光的「高级感」策略"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "多家头部展商采用白色地板 + 充足灯光的设计方案，整体视觉效果明亮、洁净、高档。这一策略投入不高但效果显著。"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "<strong>合成茵（星德科/Syntegon）展台</strong>：设计极为简洁，但利用大面积的品牌色彩（蓝色）形成强烈的视觉辨识度，灯光充足，展台整体非常明亮。简洁≠简陋，关键在于色彩的统一性和灯光覆盖度。"
    },
    {
      "type": "html",
      "text": "<img src=\"image/propak-summary/星德科展台设计很简单 但很亮 大片色彩很有辨识度.jpg\" alt=\"星德科展台：简洁设计+大片蓝+充足灯光\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:8px;margin:12px 0;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\">"
    },
    {
      "type": "html",
      "text": "<div style=\"display:flex;gap:12px;margin:12px 0;flex-wrap:wrap\"><div style=\"flex:1;min-width:200px\"><img src=\"image/propak-summary/星德科展台设计很简单 但很亮 大片色彩很有辨识度 2.jpg\" alt=\"星德科展台侧面\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\"><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#999;margin-top:4px;text-align:center\">星德科展台侧面</p></div><div style=\"flex:1;min-width:200px\"><img src=\"image/propak-summary/星德科展台设计很简单 但很亮 大片色彩很有辨识度 3.jpg\" alt=\"星德科展台整体\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\"><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#999;margin-top:4px;text-align:center\">星德科展台整体</p></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "<strong>IMA 展台</strong>：灯光充足，白色地板，整体明亮高档。顶部灯光布局覆盖整个展台区域，无暗角。"
    },
    {
      "type": "html",
      "text": "<div style=\"display:flex;gap:12px;margin:12px 0;flex-wrap:wrap\"><div style=\"flex:1;min-width:200px\"><img src=\"image/propak-summary/IMA 展台 灯光充足 白色地板 显得亮 高档.jpg\" alt=\"IMA展台整体\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\"><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#999;margin-top:4px;text-align:center\">IMA展台整体</p></div><div style=\"flex:1;min-width:200px\"><img src=\"image/propak-summary/IMA 展台 灯光充足 白色地板 显得亮 高档 2.jpg\" alt=\"IMA展台内部灯光\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\"><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#999;margin-top:4px;text-align:center\">IMA展台内部灯光</p></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "<strong>Eiahe 展台</strong>：白色展台搭配明亮灯光，显得高端大气。"
    },
    {
      "type": "html",
      "text": "<div style=\"display:flex;gap:12px;margin:12px 0;flex-wrap:wrap\"><div style=\"flex:1;min-width:200px\"><img src=\"image/propak-summary/Eiahe白色的展台显得很亮高档.jpg\" alt=\"Eiahe白色展台正面\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\"><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#999;margin-top:4px;text-align:center\">Eiahe白色展台正面</p></div><div style=\"flex:1;min-width:200px\"><img src=\"image/propak-summary/Eiahe白色的展台显得很亮高档 2.jpg\" alt=\"Eiahe白色展台侧面\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\"><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#999;margin-top:4px;text-align:center\">Eiahe白色展台侧面</p></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "<strong>GEA 展台</strong>：白色展台，地台还做了灯光装饰，视觉效果更加高档。地台灯光是一种成本可控但效果显著的设计手法。"
    },
    {
      "type": "html",
      "text": "<img src=\"image/propak-summary/GEA 展台 白色 地台还做了灯光 看起来高档.jpg\" alt=\"GEA展台白色地台灯光\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:8px;margin:12px 0;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\">"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "<strong>保立隆展台</strong>：同样采用灯光充足+白色地板的策略，整体明亮高档。"
    },
    {
      "type": "html",
      "text": "<img src=\"image/propak-summary/保立隆展台 灯光充足 白色地板 显得亮 高档.jpg\" alt=\"保立隆展台灯光效果\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:8px;margin:12px 0;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\">"
    },
    {
      "type": "h3",
      "text": "1.2 反面案例：暗淡与拥挤"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "个别展台灯光不足导致整体暗淡，或设备摆放过多造成拥挤感，直接降低了观众进入意愿。"
    },
    {
      "type": "html",
      "text": "<div style=\"display:flex;gap:12px;margin:12px 0;flex-wrap:wrap\"><div style=\"flex:1;min-width:200px\"><img src=\"image/propak-summary/展台暗淡.jpg\" alt=\"展台暗淡无光（反面案例）\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\"><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#999;margin-top:4px;text-align:center\">展台暗淡无光（反面案例）</p></div><div style=\"flex:1;min-width:200px\"><img src=\"image/propak-summary/展台设备摆太多很拥挤 没有向进入的欲望.jpg\" alt=\"设备过多导致拥挤（反面案例）\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\"><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#999;margin-top:4px;text-align:center\">设备过多导致拥挤（反面案例）</p></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "type": "h3",
      "text": "1.3 吊旗与顶部装饰光照"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "吊旗是展台视觉的重要元素。多家展商在吊旗上增加灯光照射，使展台在远处就能被清晰识别。"
    },
    {
      "type": "html",
      "text": "<div style=\"display:flex;gap:12px;margin:12px 0;flex-wrap:wrap\"><div style=\"flex:1;min-width:200px\"><img src=\"image/propak-summary/吊旗在展台里很显眼.jpg\" alt=\"吊旗在展台内很显眼\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\"><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#999;margin-top:4px;text-align:center\">吊旗在展台内很显眼</p></div><div style=\"flex:1;min-width:200px\"><img src=\"image/propak-summary/吊旗在展台里很显眼 2.jpg\" alt=\"吊旗效果侧面\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\"><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#999;margin-top:4px;text-align:center\">吊旗效果侧面</p></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "type": "html",
      "text": "<div style=\"display:flex;gap:12px;margin:12px 0;flex-wrap:wrap\"><div style=\"flex:1;min-width:200px\"><img src=\"image/propak-summary/吊旗上挂灯打光 效果很好.jpg\" alt=\"吊旗挂灯照明效果\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\"><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#999;margin-top:4px;text-align:center\">吊旗挂灯照明效果</p></div><div style=\"flex:1;min-width:200px\"><img src=\"image/propak-summary/吊旗做光照 展台很亮.jpg\" alt=\"吊旗光照使展台明亮\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\"><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#999;margin-top:4px;text-align:center\">吊旗光照使展台明亮</p></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "type": "html",
      "text": "<div style=\"display:flex;gap:12px;margin:12px 0;flex-wrap:wrap\"><div style=\"flex:1;min-width:200px\"><img src=\"image/propak-summary/吊装广告牌补光 展台很亮.jpg\" alt=\"吊装广告牌补光\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\"><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#999;margin-top:4px;text-align:center\">吊装广告牌补光</p></div><div style=\"flex:1;min-width:200px\"><img src=\"image/propak-summary/吊旗造型做的很复杂.jpg\" alt=\"复杂造型吊旗（成本较高）\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\"><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#999;margin-top:4px;text-align:center\">复杂造型吊旗（成本较高）</p></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "type": "h3",
      "text": "1.4 立柱灯光设计"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "立柱打光是展会设计的常见手法，可以有效提升展台科技感和辨识度，同时起到空间划分作用。"
    },
    {
      "type": "html",
      "text": "<div style=\"display:flex;gap:12px;margin:12px 0;flex-wrap:wrap\"><div style=\"flex:1;min-width:200px\"><img src=\"image/propak-summary/立柱灯参考.jpg\" alt=\"立柱灯参考\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\"><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#999;margin-top:4px;text-align:center\">立柱灯参考</p></div><div style=\"flex:1;min-width:200px\"><img src=\"image/propak-summary/立柱打光参考.jpg\" alt=\"立柱打光效果\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\"><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#999;margin-top:4px;text-align:center\">立柱打光效果</p></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "type": "html",
      "text": "<img src=\"image/propak-summary/立柱打灯效果还行.jpg\" alt=\"立柱打灯效果\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:8px;margin:12px 0;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\">"
    },
    {
      "type": "h3",
      "text": "1.5 空间布局参考"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "<strong>前面空旷+后面座位</strong>：利用立柱灯光进行空间划分，前面留给设备和展示，后面安排洽谈座位，动线清晰。"
    },
    {
      "type": "html",
      "text": "<div style=\"display:flex;gap:12px;margin:12px 0;flex-wrap:wrap\"><div style=\"flex:1;min-width:200px\"><img src=\"image/propak-summary/展台前面空旷 后面放座位 用立柱灯光 设计思路参考.jpg\" alt=\"展台前空后坐布局1\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\"><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#999;margin-top:4px;text-align:center\">展台前空后坐布局1</p></div><div style=\"flex:1;min-width:200px\"><img src=\"image/propak-summary/展台前面空旷 后面放座位 用立柱灯光 设计思路参考 2.jpg\" alt=\"展台前空后坐布局2\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\"><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#999;margin-top:4px;text-align:center\">展台前空后坐布局2</p></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "<strong>二层做接待</strong>：将接待区放在二层，有效利用纵向空间，同时提升展台层次感。"
    },
    {
      "type": "html",
      "text": "<img src=\"image/propak-summary/二层做接待的设计效果.jpg\" alt=\"二层接待区设计\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:8px;margin:12px 0;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\">"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "<strong>岛台兼储物间</strong>：中央岛台下面设置为储物空间，解决了展台收纳问题。"
    },
    {
      "type": "html",
      "text": "<img src=\"image/propak-summary/岛台在中间兼做储物间.jpg\" alt=\"岛台兼储物间设计\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:8px;margin:12px 0;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\">"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "<strong>斜面的展柜不太实用</strong>：斜面的陈列柜虽然新颖，但实际展示效果不佳，物品容易滑落且不方便观看。"
    },
    {
      "type": "html",
      "text": "<img src=\"image/propak-summary/斜面的展柜不太实用.jpg\" alt=\"斜面展柜（不推荐）\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:8px;margin:12px 0;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\">"
    },
    {
      "type": "h2",
      "text": "二、搭建与物流"
    },
    {
      "type": "h3",
      "text": "2.1 设备进场时机"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "核心经验：<strong>设备进场越早越好</strong>。如果进场晚，其他展位搭建完毕后叉车无法通过，只能依靠人力搬运，耗时耗力且存在安全风险。"
    },
    {
      "type": "html",
      "text": "<div style=\"display:flex;gap:12px;margin:12px 0;flex-wrap:wrap\"><div style=\"flex:1;min-width:200px\"><img src=\"image/propak-summary/设备进场越早越好 防止其他展位搭好了叉车不好进.jpg\" alt=\"设备进场通道拥挤\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\"><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#999;margin-top:4px;text-align:center\">设备进场通道拥挤</p></div><div style=\"flex:1;min-width:200px\"><img src=\"image/propak-summary/第一天展台搭建进度.jpg\" alt=\"第一天搭建进度\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\"><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#999;margin-top:4px;text-align:center\">第一天搭建进度</p></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "type": "h3",
      "text": "2.2 运输包装方案"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "建议之后展会统一采用<strong>硬质箱子+托盘</strong>的打包方案，一方面保护设备，另一方面减少每次需要搬运多个小箱子的麻烦。托盘方便叉车操作，尤其适合海外展会需要多次转运的场景。"
    },
    {
      "type": "html",
      "text": "<div style=\"display:flex;gap:12px;margin:12px 0;flex-wrap:wrap\"><div style=\"flex:1;min-width:200px\"><img src=\"image/propak-summary/准备硬质箱子加托盘 省的每次都要很多小箱子麻烦 1.jpg\" alt=\"硬质箱+托盘方案1\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\"><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#999;margin-top:4px;text-align:center\">硬质箱+托盘方案1</p></div><div style=\"flex:1;min-width:200px\"><img src=\"image/propak-summary/准备硬质箱子加托盘 省的每次都要很多小箱子麻烦 2.jpg\" alt=\"硬质箱+托盘方案2\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\"><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#999;margin-top:4px;text-align:center\">硬质箱+托盘方案2</p></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "<strong>设备木箱发货单</strong>需要妥善保存，用于海关报关和设备追踪。"
    },
    {
      "type": "html",
      "text": "<div style=\"display:flex;gap:12px;margin:12px 0;flex-wrap:wrap\"><div style=\"flex:1;min-width:200px\"><img src=\"image/propak-summary/设备木箱发货单 1.jpg\" alt=\"设备木箱发货单1\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\"><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#999;margin-top:4px;text-align:center\">设备木箱发货单1</p></div><div style=\"flex:1;min-width:200px\"><img src=\"image/propak-summary/设备木箱发货单 2.jpg\" alt=\"设备木箱发货单2\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\"><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#999;margin-top:4px;text-align:center\">设备木箱发货单2</p></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "type": "h3",
      "text": "2.3 展馆区域参考"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "H1 馆左侧以低质量标摊和小型条包机厂商为主，H3 右侧多为小标摊。未来选展位时应优先避开这些低质量区域，尽量靠近主通道和头部展商。"
    },
    {
      "type": "html",
      "text": "<div style=\"display:flex;gap:12px;margin:12px 0;flex-wrap:wrap\"><div style=\"flex:1;min-width:200px\"><img src=\"image/propak-summary/H1 馆左侧低质量标摊.jpg\" alt=\"H1馆左侧低质量标摊\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\"><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#999;margin-top:4px;text-align:center\">H1馆左侧低质量标摊</p></div><div style=\"flex:1;min-width:200px\"><img src=\"image/propak-summary/H3 右侧都是小标摊.jpg\" alt=\"H3右侧小标摊\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"width:100%;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\"><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:#999;margin-top:4px;text-align:center\">H3右侧小标摊</p></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "type": "html",
      "text": "<img src=\"image/propak-summary/H1 馆左侧条包机厂商.jpg\" alt=\"H1馆条包机厂商\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:8px;margin:12px 0;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\">"
    },
    {
      "type": "h2",
      "text": "三、电气与设备"
    },
    {
      "type": "h3",
      "text": "3.1 设备接电规范"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "泰国场馆对电气安全要求严格，有两个关键规则必须遵守："
    },
    {
      "type": "ol",
      "items": [
        "<strong>必须使用 Y 形端子</strong>：不可使用裸线或非标端子连接电源，否则场馆方不给送电。需要提前准备各种规格的 Y 形端子。",
        "<strong>不可以拆除展商的电箱</strong>：直接拆除展商提供的电箱接线属于违规行为，场馆方发现后将拒绝送电。必须通过合规方式接入。"
      ]
    },
